        <li>Seasonal recipes tested in real homes</li>
        <li>Ayurvedic food wisdom tailored for today</li>
        <li>Interactive workshops and kitchen experiments</li>
        <li>Open sourcing stories and lab-backed truth</li>
      </ul>

